title: Baby of fallen soldier meets father's unit for special photoshoot
content: Jun 02, 2018  Christian Michelle Harris, the baby daughter of fallen U.S. Army Spc. Chris Harris, helped honor her father’s memory with a special photoshoot recently. Harris was killed in Afghanistan last August when a suicide bomber attacked a NATO convoy.   Pinehurst Photography via Storyful
